'''''Desires of the Heart''''' is a 2008 Chinese [[romantic comedy]] film directed and written by [[Ma Liwen]], starring [[Vivian Wu]], [[Ge You]], [[Fan Bingbing]], and Cong Shan.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chinesemov.com/2008/Desires%20of%20the%20Heart.html |title=Desires of the Heart (2008) |date= |publisher= |work= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lovehkfilm.com/panasia/desires_of_the_heart.html |title=Desires of the Heart|date= |publisher= |work= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.topchinesemovies.com/desires-of-the-heart/ |title=Desires of the Heart |date= |publisher= |work= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cultural-china.com/20081126133329.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502002924/http://news.cultural-china.com/20081126133329.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2014-05-02 |title="Desires of the Heart" in promotion in Xi´an |date=2008 |publisher= |work=Cultural China}}</ref> The film was first released in China on 20 November 2008, and grossed over ￥20 million.

==Cast==
* [[Vivian Wu]] as Ye Shengying.
* [[Ge You]] as the swindler who cheats women.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.china.org.cn/culture/2009-08/04/content_18263775.htm |title=Ge You: 'Maybe I look like a liar' |date=2009 |publisher= |work=China.org}}</ref>
* [[Fan Bingbing]] as a woman with a pair of glasses who was cheated by the swindler.
* Cong Shan as a woman who was cheated by the swindler.

===Other===
*[[Chen Jin (actress)|Chen Jin]] as a middle-aged women who was cheated by the swindler.
*[[Guo Tao (actor)|Guo Tao]] as Zhang Su.
*[[Yuen Qiu]] as Gao Yajuan.
*[[Mei Ting]] as Zhang Ying.
*Geng Le as Zhao Da.
*[[Song Jia (actress, born 1980)|Song Jia]] as Lin Cong.
*[[Li Chen (actor)|Li Chen]] as Guan Xiang.
*[[Li Xiaolu]] as Xiao Mei.
*Duan Yihong as Zong Yang.
*[[Liu Zhenyun]] as Wei Xiang, Ye Shengying's former husband.
*Baty Chen as Wei Xiang's lover.
*Li Na as Zhang Ying's girlfriend.
*Gao Fei as Zhang Ying's girlfriend.

==Box office==
It grossed ￥2 million on its first day,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://yule.sohu.com/20081202/n260981457.shtml |script-title=zh:11.23内地电影票房：《桃花运》大热北方 |date=2008 |publisher= |work=Sohu |language=zh }}</ref> and it grossed ￥20 million on its opening weekend.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2008-11-27/03492269033.shtml |script-title=zh:《桃花运》票房破2000万打赢首轮"贺岁战" |date=2008 |publisher= |work=Sina |language=zh }}</ref>

